{"tid":757463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【令人心酸】筵開170圍新郎卻走佬 新娘獨自向賓客道歉","createTime":"2018-07-27T01:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T01:43:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc812ba59280db9e3899ec9b8f051ce4193b20c","tid":757463,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T01:18:37.000Z","msg":"泰國叻丕府一場婚宴筵開170席，場面盛大，沒料到宴會尚未開始，新娘竟穿着婚紗獨自上台鞠躬道歉，並冷靜地宣佈新郎「已走佬」。<br />\n<br />\n從台下賓客拍攝的短片可見，24歲新娘的聲線原本非常冷靜，她感謝親友出席婚宴，並對自己招待不周鞠躬道歉。她亦稱沒料到事情會變成這樣，後來聲音開始顫抖，一名女親友亦上台安慰及支持她。<br />\n<br />\n據女親友的說法，新娘和20歲新郎決定結婚後有拍攝婚照，不過婚禮舉行前一星期，新娘才知道新郎另有情人，當時新郎還堅持要娶新娘過門。到了婚禮前2天，新郎又傳短訊稱無法負擔20萬泰銖（約4.7萬港元）和等值金飾的聘禮，即使女方家人願意資助14萬泰銖（約3.3萬港元），新郎也繼續「玩失蹤」，直至婚禮前一晚大約11時，男方家人也通知女方婚禮將如常舉行。<br />\n<br />\n然而新郎最終沒有現身，女方家人一度請求新郎叔叔假扮新郎，好讓新娘不用太難堪，但叔叔要求100萬泰銖（約23.5萬港元）做報酬，女方惟有作罷，新娘也只好上台講述新郎逃婚的詳情。<br />\n<br />\n叔叔其後在fb表示，找人假扮新郎的要求太荒謬，所以才「獅子開大口」嚇走女方家人，又稱新郎其實不愛新娘、是新娘迫婚云云。不過網民普遍同情新娘，認為男家的行為太過份，消息指新娘已就新郎逃婚報警處理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/091827_afb39fe3f125bffa9ecad7a3f9e7f958.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F091827_afb39fe3f125bffa9ecad7a3f9e7f958.png&h=306b5c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180726/58487357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F58487357&d=UAQ9pE%2FGVdgdJKmfP0crvhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=48fdec2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F58487357&h=463dce2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180726/58487357</a>"},{"pid":"a646e129696f86093f0db0504cf68c7dda6f1f4c","tid":757463,"uid":173043,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T01:29:06.000Z","msg":"d 相打晒格，好難討論"},{"pid":"c1f2c8a2eab199649b6ec79f512f2fc045b77786","tid":757463,"uid":32051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T01:31:43.000Z","msg":"只有樣貌可以猜測可能<br />\n但無樣，咁同content farm有咩分別<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a2752b75c21b52e3965612a15a9243afc3dae6","tid":757463,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:00:04.000Z","msg":"點解要搵叔叔假扮, 求其請個臨記咪得"},{"pid":"48f728347a1c86e7707bc02f21943ba4412789c1","tid":757463,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:02:48.000Z","msg":"講到尾咩都係錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2313e83fac90160ac1bd91f633b032bc4a703b","tid":757463,"uid":90818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"有link<br />\n<br />\n[url]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7832ab5db5d1b41ac6487dd2200b2aa7e4b5f3","tid":757463,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55b3072d624a137fd1c33544729ad8e6710c15e9","tid":757463,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:43:38.000Z","msg":"新娘樣都唔算差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新郎噉都要走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fd8a12e45265d55c9b213245a3fda1b181029d","tid":757463,"uid":194474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:50:13.000Z","msg":"逃婚就可以報警？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea315d7ebe69f665c257f3146c524612cd5f701e","tid":757463,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"Fb Manow Jutathip Nimnual"},{"pid":"5ca1b5dd0